video_info.title: FULL SPEECH: Trump holds rally on Long Island  | LiveNOW from FOX
video_info.description:
Former President Donald Trump delivered remarks at a campaign rally in Uniondale, New York Wednesday evening.

The rally took place on the same day Trump was initially supposed to be sentenced in his New York hush money case. 

Judge Juan Merchan delayed the sentencing to November 26, until after the election.
